<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="please-v">please <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pliːz/    美 /pliːz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 高兴；(使) 满意；讨好：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It pleases me that he should want to talk about his worries.
他愿和我谈谈他的烦心事，我很高兴。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>is hard to please</strong>. Everything has to be perfect.
让她满意很难，一切都得完美才行。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>喜欢；愿意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You may stay as long <strong>as you please</strong>. 
你想待多久就待多久。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>pleasing /'pliːzɪŋ/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a design that is <strong>pleasing to the eye</strong>
悦目的设计</p></div></div>